I'm comparing two netlists through equiv_make given as below:
**First netlist:**

```
module inverter(in, out);
input in;
wire in;
output out;
wire out;
sky130_fd_sc_hd__inv_2 0 (
.A(in),
.Y(out)
);
endmodule
```

**second_netlist**

```
module inverter (in,
out);
